London Subway Says Bombardier Preferred Overhaul Bidder, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-04-13T01:41:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/london-subway-says-bombardier-preferred-overhaul-bidder-ft-says.html
London Underground identified
Bombardier Transportation Inc. as the preferred bidder to
overhaul the signaling system on about 40 percent of the subway
network, the Financial Times reported, citing London Underground
Managing Director  Mike Brown .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 